sequenceDiagram
accTitle: Mermaid activation flow defaults
accDescr {
Demonstrates the default Mermaid-to-sequencer activation policy where calls keep the callee active until a return.
From the project root, regenerate this Mermaid transform and SVG with:
node sequencer.js --mermaid -i test/mermaid-features/13-activation-flow-defaults/input.mmd -o -f -t test/mermaid-features/13-activation-flow-defaults
}
participant Caller
participant Service
participant DB
Caller->>Service: Submit request [Mermaid: Caller->>Service: Submit request]
Service->>DB: Persist data [Mermaid: Service->>DB: Persist data]
DB-->>Service: Persistence complete [Mermaid: DB-->>Service: Persistence complete]
Service-->>Caller: Reply to caller [Mermaid: Service-->>Caller: Reply to caller]
